<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="15Jun1939"><font color="red">15 June 1939</font> <i>NLFF</i> (from Richard de la Mere to Paul L&eacute;on): But, since Mr Joyce feels so strongly on this point, we are going to reconsider <i>The Irish Times</i> for an advertisement &hellip; in the current issue of <i>The Bookseller</i> &hellip; it is listed as being among the first twelve best-sellers. </div>
